During experimentation with active fault detection, to avoid delays in the convergence of the estimated pretension to the reference value, the UKF algorithm is restarted after each pretension change, with the expected pretension as the initial value. The UKF algorithm was internally parameterized based on the recommendations from [32]. The measurement noise covariance was set to \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
