				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$P=25\%$$\end{document}P=25%). Furthermore a compensated fault condition was set when the control strategy utilizes the actual value of P for calculations, and an uncompensated fault condition was set by utilizing the initial pretension (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
